Mia Kruger from Kruger International chose Google as her stock pick of the day and Nick Crail from Ashburton Investments chose Alibaba. Kruger said: “I would choose the technology companies at this stage as their prices have also come back a bit with the rest of the market. Google, with its strong advertising, is a strong player in the online sector.” Crail said: “My pick is technology, it is global and for [me] it’s Alibaba.” Or listen to the full audio: Subscribe: iono.fm | Apple Podcasts | Pocket Casts | Player.fm